cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NA 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories as it deals with structure detection and multiview stereo matching. It also involves optimization techniques, which could place it in the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the use of Markov random fields suggests that it could also belong to the numerical analysis (cs.NA) sub-category.
